BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260405T064800
DTEND:20260405T130000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.174ft at 06:48\n-2.998ft at 13:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Primarily long-period\, selective S swell getting in\, along with a little
  NW swell. Good summertime breaks are running waist to chest high\, as sta
 ndouts hit head high. Dawn patrol drained some by a negative low tide\, th
 en incoming tide push gets an assist for the rest of the morning. \n\nLigh
 t winds due all day\, offshore most of the morning\, WSW breeze in the aft
 ernoon. 
END:VEVENT
