DTSTART:20260406T064800
DTEND:20260406T144200
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.663ft at 06:48\n-2.993ft at 14:42\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Continued long-period\, selective S swell rolling in\, along with a little
  lingering NW swell\, maintaining waist to chest high waves at exposures\,
  while standouts go head high. Favorable tide push most of the morning. \n
 \nLight winds due all day\, offshore most of the morning\, followed by a W
  sea breeze in the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
